Foot and mouth disease, Korea (Rep of)
--------------------------------------
Information (dated 19 Apr 2010) received on 20 Apr 2010 from Dr Kiyoon
Chang, CVO & Director, Labelling, Quarantine and Inspection Division, Food
Safety & Consumer Affairs Policy Bureau, MIFAFF (Ministry of Food,
Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries), Gyeonggi-Do, Korea (Rep of)

Summary
Report type: follow-up report no. 1
Start date: 8 Apr 2010
Date of 1st confirmation of the event: 9 Apr 2010
Date submitted to OIE: 20 Apr 2010
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 11 Mar 2010
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: Foot and mouth disease virus
Serotype O
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

